==English==

===Interjection===
'''meh'''

# An onomatopoeia expressing [[indifference]] or [[apathy]]; the verbal equivalent of a shrug of the shoulders
#: ''"What do you want for dinner?" &mdash; "Meh."''
# Also can be used for "[[I don't know]]".

-Widely used due to popular show The Simpsons, where "meh" is used by Lenny.
